data.name: aboutLabel.Text
data.value:
Clarifies the image using a magic blend of hq4x passes, antialiasing, bicubic interpolation, crossfading, tiling and soft gaussian blur. Applies to both the original image ("before") and the resultant image ("after"): -Use the left mouse button to resize. -Use the right mouse button to move.
